Package com.airs.visualisations

Class Summary
MapViewerActivity Activity to view the GI/VI sensors on a Google Map view
MapViewerOverlay Class to implement the overlay of GI/VI sensors in the Map View
MapViewerOverlayTrack Class for the overlay track being shown for the GI/VI sensors
TimelineActivity Class to implement a timeline view for all sensors that support it.
TimelineView Class to implement a timeline with two colors and a grid
